<section class="portrait-demo" aria-label="人像站位与裁切示意图">
  <div class="portrait-demo__grid">
    <div class="portrait-demo__card">
      <div class="portrait-demo__badge">半身更稳</div>
      <div class="portrait-demo__frame portrait-demo__frame--half">
        <div class="portrait-demo__person portrait-demo__person--half">
          <div class="portrait-demo__head"></div>
          <div class="portrait-demo__body"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="portrait-demo__mark portrait-demo__mark--half">胸口以上</div>
      </div>
      <p>半身最适合初学者练习表情、眼神和背景整理，成功率高，也最容易看出光和构图有没有帮到人物。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="portrait-demo__card">
      <div class="portrait-demo__badge">环境人像看关系</div>
      <div class="portrait-demo__frame portrait-demo__frame--env">
        <div class="portrait-demo__person portrait-demo__person--env">
          <div class="portrait-demo__head"></div>
          <div class="portrait-demo__body"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="portrait-demo__env env-left">背景</div>
        <div class="portrait-demo__env env-right">留给环境</div>
      </div>
      <p>环境人像不是把人缩小就行，而是让人物和环境之间有明确关系，环境是在补充人物，不是在抢戏。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

